{
  "stem": "20575.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we stayed in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nothing to say.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- it-- it-- you-- there the Jewish leaders were kind of silenced because you were nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You became nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no more Jewish leaders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was called the [NON-ENGLISH], where they have, like, the organization of-- of the Jews who took care of the cemeteries and all this things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I guess people used to pay dues to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it ended. '38 was-- and '39, and then everybody was dispersed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People tried to get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People to-- to-- to-- tried to just hope that the world will-- is not going to let it happen, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Especially my father was the biggest optimist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, no way will he get away with this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We just lived our life from one day to the other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "First, one time is that my-- we were supposed to go to England, my brother and I, to Glasgow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To Scotland.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they tried to initiate that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then the [INAUDIBLE]-- the last thing was, again, look.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We're staying together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Whatever happens to us, will happen to all of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They couldn't-- we couldn't part.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because we were children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I guess my parents didn't have the heart to-- to just-- [INAUDIBLE] it was just initiated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was not actually happening yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we didn't pursue it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because my father said, my mother said, whatever happen, we'll stay together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Not knowing what's going to happen anyhow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the beginning, yes, I would say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because like I said, we just walked over to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had-- we might not have had the same food or something, but-- in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
